  "detailed_description": "<strong>One True Hero</strong> is a quirky <strong>3D platforming adventure</strong> featuring a young hero who can barely save himself!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An Epic Adventure</strong></h2>​An evil tyrant... A magic sword... A young farmer turned <strong>Hero</strong>...<br>It's a tale we've heard thousands of times before, and in the kingdom of Genericia things like that happen every other week! <br>This makes it hard for our Hero to be taken seriously when he tries to save a town that's mysteriously sinking into the ground, even if he is the only one capable of saving it!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/63e1febbd711f08cb45a8dcd299f8d1e.poster.avif?t=1706800488\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/63e1febbd711f08cb45a8dcd299f8d1e.webm?t=1706800488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/63e1febbd711f08cb45a8dcd299f8d1e.mp4?t=1706800488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Nerve-Racking Sword Fights</strong></h2>All sorts of terrible evil creatures will stand in your path. You're going to have to deal with them if you want to save the kingdom!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/3c08fcc97fdc90d6231641950d32b49c.poster.avif?t=1706800488\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/3c08fcc97fdc90d6231641950d32b49c.webm?t=1706800488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/3c08fcc97fdc90d6231641950d32b49c.mp4?t=1706800488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Loads of Platforming</strong></h2>Who knew there was so much jumping involved in being a legendary hero?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/231492f1b91d669457967211051e311e.poster.avif?t=1706800488\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/231492f1b91d669457967211051e311e.webm?t=1706800488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/231492f1b91d669457967211051e311e.mp4?t=1706800488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Tale to Remember</strong></h2>Meet a cast of memorable characters, explore dungeons, solve puzzles and unravel the mystery of the sinking town before it disappears off the face of the earth!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/4ed65924cf07529083f87d8008eefbde.poster.avif?t=1706800488\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/4ed65924cf07529083f87d8008eefbde.webm?t=1706800488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/4ed65924cf07529083f87d8008eefbde.mp4?t=1706800488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Will you be the One True Hero this kingdom needs?</strong></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>One True Hero</strong> is a quirky <strong>3D platforming adventure</strong> featuring a young hero who can barely save himself!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An Epic Adventure</strong></h2>​An evil tyrant... A magic sword... A young farmer turned <strong>Hero</strong>...<br>It's a tale we've heard thousands of times before, and in the kingdom of Genericia things like that happen every other week! <br>This makes it hard for our Hero to be taken seriously when he tries to save a town that's mysteriously sinking into the ground, even if he is the only one capable of saving it!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/63e1febbd711f08cb45a8dcd299f8d1e.poster.avif?t=1706800488\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/63e1febbd711f08cb45a8dcd299f8d1e.webm?t=1706800488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/63e1febbd711f08cb45a8dcd299f8d1e.mp4?t=1706800488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Nerve-Racking Sword Fights</strong></h2>All sorts of terrible evil creatures will stand in your path. You're going to have to deal with them if you want to save the kingdom!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/3c08fcc97fdc90d6231641950d32b49c.poster.avif?t=1706800488\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/3c08fcc97fdc90d6231641950d32b49c.webm?t=1706800488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596170/extras/3c08fcc97fdc90d62316